{%- comment -%}
  HeiPard — Versand- & Lieferzeit-Hinweis unter dem PDP-Preis.

  Zeigt drei Zeilen:
    1. Inkl. MwSt. (nur wenn Steuern im Preis enthalten sind)
    2. Versandkosten werden im Checkout berechnet (verlinkt Versand-Policy, falls vorhanden)
    3. Lieferzeit — abhaengig von der aktuell gewaehlten Versandzone des Kunden

  Zonen-Erkennung ueber Shopify Markets (`localization.country`):
    - Inland:     DE
    - EU-Ausland: alle uebrigen EU-Laender (ISO-Liste unten)
    - Welt:       alle anderen Laender

  Lieferzeit-Texte sind ueber die Section-Settings konfigurierbar
  (delivery_domestic / delivery_eu / delivery_world) und fallen sonst
  auf sinnvolle Defaults zurueck.

  Akzeptierte Parameter:
    delivery_domestic, delivery_eu, delivery_world (String, optional)
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- liquid
  assign zone = 'world'
  assign cc = localization.country.iso_code | default: shop.address.country_code

  if cc == 'DE'
    assign zone = 'domestic'
  else
    assign eu_codes = 'AT,BE,BG,HR,CY,CZ,DK,EE,FI,FR,GR,HU,IE,IT,LV,LT,LU,MT,NL,PL,PT,RO,SK,SI,ES,SE'
    assign eu_list = eu_codes | split: ','
    if eu_list contains cc
      assign zone = 'eu'
    endif
  endif

  assign txt_domestic = delivery_domestic | default: '1–3 Werktage'
  assign txt_eu = delivery_eu | default: '3–10 Werktage'
  assign txt_world = delivery_world | default: '5–15 Werktage'

  case zone
    when 'domestic'
      assign delivery_value = txt_domestic
    when 'eu'
      assign delivery_value = txt_eu
    else
      assign delivery_value = txt_world
  endcase
-%}

<div class="heipard-shipping-note">
  {%- if cart.taxes_included -%}
    <p class="heipard-shipping-note__row">
      <span class="heipard-shipping-note__icon" aria-hidden="true">
        {{- 'icon-info.svg' | inline_asset_content -}}
      </span>
      <span>{{ 'products.product.heipard.tax_included' | t }}</span>
    </p>
  {%- endif -%}

  <p class="heipard-shipping-note__row">
    <span class="heipard-shipping-note__icon" aria-hidden="true">
      {{- 'icon-truck.svg' | inline_asset_content -}}
    </span>
    <span>
      {%- if shop.shipping_policy.url != blank -%}
        <a class="heipard-shipping-note__link" href="{{ shop.shipping_policy.url }}">{{ 'products.product.heipard.shipping_costs' | t }}</a>
        {{ 'products.product.heipard.shipping_at_checkout' | t }}
      {%- else -%}
        {{ 'products.product.heipard.shipping_costs' | t }} {{ 'products.product.heipard.shipping_at_checkout' | t }}
      {%- endif -%}
    </span>
  </p>

  <p class="heipard-shipping-note__row">
    <span class="heipard-shipping-note__icon" aria-hidden="true">
      {{- 'icon-clock.svg' | inline_asset_content -}}
    </span>
    <span>{{ 'products.product.heipard.delivery_time' | t }}: {{ delivery_value }}</span>
  </p>
</div>
